Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tajuu Kage Bunshin no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made three shadow clones this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some screech...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And the chakra's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get hit with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fuuton, Rasen-Shuriken{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:54.49,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Fuuton, Rasen-Shuriken: Wind Element, Spiraling Shuriken)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll back him up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from Naruto, or you'll get caught in the blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Kyuubi Jinchuuriki's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fitting technique for a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shi-!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did he get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lost it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.18,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,mijika ni arumono
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.18,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be extra careful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.52,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,tsune ni ki wo tsuketeinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.52,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,with the things nearest to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.44,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,amari ni chikasugite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.44,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the closer you get to something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.40,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,miushinatteshimaisou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.40,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the tougher it is to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.95,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,anata ga saikin taiken shita
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.95,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain to me this happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.87,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,shiawase wa ittai nan desu ka{\b1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.87,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,that you just got to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.71,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,megumaresugeteite
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.71,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you're so blessed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.53,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,omoidasenai kamo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.53,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,that you can't even remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.42,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,ima koko ni iru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.42,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,That you stand here now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:12.26,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,iki wo shiteiru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:12.26,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,That you live and breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:15.30,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,tada sore dake no koto ga
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:15.30,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all little miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.78,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,kiseki da to kizuku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.78,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,just by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.68,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,mijika ni arumono
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.68,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be extra careful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:22.81,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,tsune ni ki wo tsuketeinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:22.81,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,with the things nearest to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:25.73,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,amari ni chikasugite
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:25.73,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the closer you get to something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.40,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,miushinatteshimaisou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.40,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the tougher it is to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:31.78,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the closer you get to something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:34.28,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the tougher it is to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.99,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll never take it for granted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.79,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,oitsuzuketekita yume
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.79,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine to say "Never give up."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:43.29,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,akiramezuni susume yo nante
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:43.29,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,and "Keep chasing your dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:46.04,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,kirei koto wo ieru hodo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:46.04,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,But the more time you spend talking big
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.71,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,nanimo dekichainai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.71,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,the less you get done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:51.78,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,hitonigiri no yuuki wo mune ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:51.78,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll press that handful of courage against my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.59,OP4j,,0000,0000,0000,,ashita wo ikinuku tame ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.59,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,and with its help, survive another day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:57.55,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll never take it for granted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.93,OP4e,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,330)}Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:09.33,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\pos(769,547)\fad(660,670)}Wind Element: Rasen-Shuriken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:09.33,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HEEEEEE&\1a&H00&\bord0\fad(660,670)\pos(769,547)}Wind Element: Rasen-Shuriken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number-one most surprising ninja strikes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting tough and screwing up... I guess that was pretty Naruto-ish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it was called Rasen-Shuriken or whatever, I thought you'd throw it at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to actually get in his face and punch him with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if I'd hit him there'd be nothing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's called the Rasen-Shuriken, but it only works as a point-blank attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why its use relies on shadow clones for a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He still hasn't had enough training time. \NIf it had just lasted a couple more seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll never work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not against someone like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kyuubi kid's technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed very powerful, but I'll be fine as long as I keep my distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I avoid close-range combat and stay focused on the original body using the technique, I have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me try one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish him with my new technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going up against Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do the same thing, he'll just dodge it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll know you're trying to distract him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to fight together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, it's five against one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to cross a dangerous bridge like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what you told me when I was training?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The only shinobi who can surpass the Fourth Hokage is you."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's what I believe."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that teamwork's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also know that this is a dangerous bridge to cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cross that bridge alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't make it to the other side, I'll never be able to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't burn that bridge just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't noticed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a completely new Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pakkun, what was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really messed me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jashin {\i1}will{\i0} punish you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll bring His great vengeance down upon you, like in the scriptures!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bullshit doesn't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you and I have very different beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in the Will of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that pathetic Lord Jashin or whatever isn't your God anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one bringing down vengeance is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Jashinist scripture says He {\i1}will{\i0} smite you! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll carry out his judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My teeth are enough to take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bite you to death, motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my backup, huh? You're a few minutes too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru! Don't tell me you took out an Akatsuki all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're much more capable than I assumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was one of those things I had to do myself, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going with the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came here right away, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and rejoin them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll heal you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But-!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see any more of my friends get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sending that little snot in again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better switch to a long-range mode, just to be on the safe side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not just shape-shifting, he's drawing up a huge amount of chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be to counter Naruto's technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kage Bunshin no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can ignore the distraction shadow clones coming from the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to go after the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can eliminate his technique, there's nothing else to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! He sees through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows to attack from a distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That was a clone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He mixed himself in with the fakes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blast's coming!
