Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Boar! Dog! Rooster! Monkey! Ram!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put down your hand and...
