Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To succeed, all you need is patience, effort and training!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like Naruto could summon the Toad Boss right away, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.07,0:23:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice hard so you can master this technique!
